title: The Gavin McInnes Show 2016-10-03
description: Today on TGMS, Gavin hates East Side Dave wearing his clothes, and plays a sneak peak from his upcoming movie. Tommy Robinson Skypes in to talk about the rapper who called for his beheading. David Wygant joins Gavin in studio and they get into women, and Millennials not having sex. Baked Alaska Skypes in about NoWanks and his new Trump app. Happy Endings with Mercedes Carrera ends the show
